Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友情　戀愛　神秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那樣的約定的話就可以堅持到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歷史悠久充滿懷舊氣氛的古宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招攬遊客時有發生事件的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩  頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是鬼澤鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種好懷念從前的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.49,0:02:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫想愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是鄉愁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候換這個詞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂你們才幾歲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.89,0:02:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個據說快成為地球遺産的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是現在的話題焦點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可最近這裡因其他熱點而引起了關注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀光客也增加了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的那個其他的熱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是討厭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是幽靈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在半年之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.19,0:03:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好幾個人說看到過小孩子的幽靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是這個說法就這麼傳開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得有人以此作為解決案子的謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招待我來這裡旅遊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.69,0:03:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個好好感受充滿歷史氛圍的日本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可要享受啤酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛與幽靈與地球遺産（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越來越厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.39,0:03:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像回到了過去一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們住在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既是地球遺産又是可以投宿的民居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.79,0:03:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是歷史悠久的日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三層樓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間數比從外面看上去要多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定以前是個大家族呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.79,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的地基石頭和旁邊的土都是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.19,0:04:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是具有百年歷史的老房子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和我們一起住的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.09,0:04:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最古老的傳統式的家庭旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美子真高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼破舊的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼破有洗澡的地方嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有空調呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.09,0:04:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被他聽到的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要太過分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要給別人添麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢說我是麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了以前可饒不了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰看不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢夥是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是傢夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沈睡的小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫不得已成為了名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說迫不得已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美子太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你可是名人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐們這樣我的啤酒都灑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阪木莊吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能見到您真是我的榮幸 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫桑島和明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.19,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.99,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人您住的地方是隔壁的石岡先生那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛不早說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個石火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩魚也很鮮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的醬湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝了後身體都暖和多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天喝這個最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登這種亂七八糟的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡沒有這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對客人太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近發生了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.59,0:06:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個啊 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這篇報道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本雜誌怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球遺産村裡有幽靈出沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常出現給當地居民造成困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.49,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意外的賣點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈什麼的根本沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡給我們添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.09,0:07:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球遺産是世界的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是人類的財産
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就很了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.19,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼偉大的地方搞什麼捉鬼遊戲真是不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作為這裡的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該好好招待你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.99,0:07:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真是金玉良言啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再敬一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南我們也差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢 睡覺了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.49,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沒確認是不是真的有幽靈之前是睡不著的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是為了這個才來的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.09,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回房間看書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚去散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是很晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個也是這裡的特色啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那個出來了也不是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.09,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上這裡的人都輪流這樣巡邏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.29,0:09:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 火災是茅草屋的大敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要互相提醒小心翼翼才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個村子的人都要負責提醒互相幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經成為慣例了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 步美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡為止我們還在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是肚子餓了一個人先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又不是元太你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是步美的圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.29,0:10:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要扔下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.69,0:10:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明和她在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想還是大家一起找比較好所以就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家分頭去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.69,0:10:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家那位也是一沾上酒就停不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫村子裡的人一起找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫忙哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是醉鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在水神廟的杉樹這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼地方痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以說話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了一個女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10歲左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,童花頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著紅裙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.79,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是來找榮治的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.99,0:13:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫真美嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.29,0:13:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美和死去的榮治是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年齡只差一歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.99,0:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她相信榮治的清白所以來找他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.89,0:13:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 是你看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你不相信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美不是撒謊的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼說肯定是看錯了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都已經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,榮治在上個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩早在十年前都已經死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前就已經死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕鬼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.39,0:14:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵什麼呢 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你真是的這種時候說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是受了誰的指使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.89,0:14:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那些傢夥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會上你們的當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們稱心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且榮治這種孩子不是我的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣榮治太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給您賠罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.89,0:15:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才難得喝得那麼痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點什麼哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是幽靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有調查的價值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.19,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幽靈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乙澤家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.39,0:16:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是真美一家十年前住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是獨生女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是得病去世的吧 真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.49,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨後她的爸爸媽媽就搬到其他地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有留下照片什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了十年了不太可能了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉田看到的是不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到照片就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼真假 是說幽靈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連你也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.99,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是以理論和推理取勝的偵探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.89,0:17:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個是在問你是不是不相信吉田的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.99,0:17:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是這個叫榮治的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個永倉榮治嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.09,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說在有關犯罪的報紙裡查一查叫永倉榮治的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案子發生在半年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.59,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淨真町就是你們現在所在的鬼澤鄉旁邊的小鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現場的指紋分析出來後馬上通緝了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他是無路可逃了才自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.19,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉榮治是自殺的寶石強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.79,0:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他媽媽相信兒子是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就知道為什麼村裡的人都守口如瓶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有撒謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望至少柯南一定要相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓他調查是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.69,0:18:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣你就能安心的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.29,0:18:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一路上怎麼毛骨悚然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.59,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在剛才的地方碰到了真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.09,0:18:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是被她邀請來到了水神廟這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那以後就再也沒有出現過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.09,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我叫真美叫累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在杉樹的樹根這裡睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.49,0:19:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪裡消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說准哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霧很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在那座水神廟的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還很新呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉井 是我們路過的家庭旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件浴袍被風吹得呼啦呼拉地動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後步美就看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗完的衣服怎麼會跑到這麼遠的地方來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有看錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定看到真美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你啊 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是偶然偶然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.19,0:20:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.79,0:20:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 火燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰的腳步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來了出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是幽靈是沒有腳的啊元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們呆在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最上面一層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.39,0:21:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.49,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人還沒逃遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.09,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美你果然在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.89,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.78,0:23:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然承你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.58,0:23:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下毛利小五郎就先拔頭籌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.77,0:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是幽靈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 柯南也看到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.60,0:24:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.38,0:24:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然真正的兇手是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.50,0:24:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概今晚就會出現在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.13,0:24:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.47,0:24:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛與幽靈與地球遺產（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.90,0:24:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放大鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.30,0:24:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次是解決篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.20,0:24:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.70,0:24:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.32,0:00:25.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,近日時常夢見你突然離我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.21,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,面對惶惑不安的我 你依然無聲無息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一雙溫暖的手緊握在口袋裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.06,0:00:42.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,糾纏的五指彷彿繽紛的花朵競色爭奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.09,0:00:49.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使停駐於憂鬱隱晦的霏霏霪雨 你的身影依然那麼粲然奪目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.23,0:00:55.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向著你我約定過的溫柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.90,0:01:01.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,而今兩個人依然齊肩攀越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,遙望你為我彩繪的夢幻季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:14.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,暫別的時日可以令愛更強烈 直至歲月翻過那一頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向著你我約定過的溫柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.89,0:01:25.86,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的逃避只會迷途無措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.39,0:01:31.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,縱然漫無標識的路千曲百折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.96,0:01:39.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1450)}依循彼此的信任與愛相攜 直至步入那溫柔世界…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.77,0:22:39.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的視線相遇之前 心就已經決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.63,0:22:49.29,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如同正午的月亮一般 雖然看不見 但是知道它在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.17,0:23:01.88,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是孤獨 就算是幸福 一個人的時候又怎能分辨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.32,0:23:13.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的相遇 如同在深海中游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.06,0:23:26.41,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沐浴在光芒下呼吸 尋找我們兩人的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.64,0:23:38.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在圍繞著升起又落下的太陽 旋轉的這個星球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.28,0:23:45.01,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧緩緩起伏的海面上的月亮
